es-poppy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/grimes-poppy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grimes">格莱姆斯</a>对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/poppy">波比</a>最近重新点燃了他们多年的不和做出了回应——看看这位“Kill V. Maim”歌手在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/poppy-shares-madonna-meets-metal-single-new-way-out-and-tells-us-how-theres-plenty-to-be-angry-about-3762126">波比告诉我们“有很多事情值得生气”</a></strong></li></ul><p> Grimes 和 Poppy 的争执可以追溯到 2018 年，当时两人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-play-destroy-new-track-grimes-poppy-2395408">合作为后者的专辑“Am IA Girl？”创作了歌曲“Play Destroy”</a> 。当时，波比声称她“本可以没有”据称由她的合作者造成的麻烦。</p><p> Poppy<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/poppy-accuses-grimes-bullying-play-destroy-2415095">声称，她被 Grimes 和她的团队“胁迫屈服”</a> ，他们强迫“词曲作者签署保密协议，并且不将自己参与的歌曲归功于自己”。格莱姆斯当时回应称，这位歌手兼 YouTuber 迫使她陷入了“恶心的境地”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3576017" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3576017" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3576017" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/poppy@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/poppy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/poppy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/poppy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/poppy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/poppy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/poppy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3576017" class="wp-caption-text"> Poppy 在 2022 年雷丁表演。图片来源：Jo Hale/Redferns 摄</figcaption></figure><p>在接下来的几年里，两人多次争吵， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grimes-ignites-poppy-feud-accusing-her-of-spreading-false-information-for-personal-gain-3479509">格莱姆斯去年再次煽风点火，称波比没有证据支持她的说法</a>——波比简单地回应道：“我们还在这样做吗？哈哈。 5年触发。”</p><p>然而现在，波比再次向格莱姆斯发起攻击，这次是以算命的形式，作为她的新《副总统》系列<em>《不可思议的波比》</em>的一部分。在首播集中，波比假装是随机的公众成员的算命师。</p><p>在下面的剪辑中，波比告诉一个毫无戒心的男人：“格莱姆斯会要求你成为她孩子的代孕妈妈。说是的。但不要去赴约。如果你让她给你唱她主要唱片公司发行的任何歌曲，那就太晚了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DA8qiFvMpKH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342