me.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">The Elephant</a>将加入阵容。</p><p>上个月有报道称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-reportedly-seeking-established-acts-to-support-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793095">利亚姆·加拉格尔正在寻求“既定行为”出现在该法案中</a>。主唱此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-jokes-about-joint-blur-tour-fuels-speculation-of-manic-street-preachers-or-richard-ashcroft-supporting-oasis-3799791">建议 Manic Street Preachers 和 Richard Ashcroft 可以担任开场嘉宾</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/blossoms-interview-tom-ogden-gary-album-3796418">Blossoms 最近与<em>NME</em>讨论了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-on-supporting-oasis-if-we-get-asked-the-bags-are-packed-and-wed-smash-it-3799233">在 Live &#39;25 演出中支持 Oasis 的可能性</a>。在 Liam 在网上对这两个乐队进行猛烈抨击后，目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-doesnt-look-like-suede-will-be-supporting-oasis-on-their-reunion-tour-3795466">看来 Suede</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-on-why-they-couldnt-really-give-a-shit-about-the-oasis-reunion-3793122">Fontaines DC 不太可能出现在阵容中</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" id="291703648" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?start=1629&amp;enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" width="100%" height="392" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-gtm-yt-inspected-6="true" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-and-noel-wont-be-doing-oasis-interviews-3801412">利亚姆表示，他和诺埃尔不打算就他们期待已久的重聚进行任何采访</a>。 “我们害怕媒体问我们侵入性的问题，并试图找出我们关系中的漏洞，”他解释道。</p><p>这位主唱还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/is-liam-gallagher-teasing-us-with-a-new-oasis-album-its-already-finished-3791619">告诉歌迷，新的 Oasis 专辑“已经完成”</a> ，并向另一位歌迷重申了这一说法，写道：“它已经在袋子里了，伙计，操你的空气。”</p><p>上个月有报道称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-reportedly-seeking-established-acts-to-support-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793095">LG 正在寻找“知名艺人”为乐队在英国和爱尔兰开场</a>。此后他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-jokes-about-joint-blur-tour-fuels-speculation-of-manic-street-preachers-or-richard-ashcroft-supporting-oasis-3799791">建议疯狂街传教士和理查德·阿什克罗夫特可以担任支持职位</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/blossoms-interview-tom-ogden-gary-album-3796418">Blossoms 最近与<em>NME</em>谈论了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-on-supporting-oasis-if-we-get-asked-the-bags-are-packed-and-wed-smash-it-3799233">出现在<em>Live &#39;25</em>日期的账单上的可能性</a>。 Liam 在网上对 Suede 或 Fontaines DC 进行了猛烈抨击后，目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-doesnt-look-like-suede-will-be-supporting-oasis-on-their-reunion-tour-3795466">看来 Suede</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-on-why-they-couldnt-really-give-a-shit-about-the-oasis-reunion-3793122">Fontaines DC 不太可能出现在阵容中</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">Oasis 为澳大利亚 2025 年重聚巡演添加更多日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
埃尔维斯·科斯特洛 (Elvis Costello) 和 T Bone 在新专辑和 Audible 项目中以 Coward Brothers 身份重聚https://www.nme.com/news/music/elvis-costello-and-t-bone-reunite-as-the-coward-brothers-for-new-album-and-audible-project-3801685?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=埃尔维斯·科斯特洛和 T-Bone 重聚作为胆小鬼兄弟，参与新专辑和音频项目Laura MolloyThu, 10 Oct 2024 20:54:55 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3801685 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 1985 年，二人首次以 The Coward Brothers 身份合作拍摄单曲“The People&#39;s Limousine”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elvis-costello-and-t-bone-reunite-as-the-coward-brothers-for-new-album-and-audible-project-3801685">埃尔维斯·科斯特洛 (Elvis Costello) 和 T Bone 以 The Coward Brothers 身份重聚的新专辑和 Audible 项目</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/T-Bone-Burnett-and-Elvis-Costello.-CREDIT_-George-Pimentel_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-costello">埃尔维斯·科斯特洛 (Elvis Costello)</a>和 T Bone 再次以 The Coward Brothers 身份与 Audible 合作推出新专辑和音频系列项目。</p><p>这对搭档对合作并不陌生，伯内特共同制作了科斯特洛 1986 年的专辑“King Of America”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elvis-costello-announces-boxset-reissue-and-shares-unreleased-live-performance-of-only-daddy-thatll-walk-the-line-3799901">该专辑即将获得豪华再版</a>。在此之前，他们于 1985 年联手制作了单曲“The People&#39;s Limousine”，并以“Coward Brothers”的名义发行。</p><p>四十年后的现在，他们宣布胆小鬼兄弟带着新的喜剧播客和专辑回归。 <em>《考沃德兄弟的真实故事》</em>是一个由三部分组成的 Audible Original 音频系列，将讲述流行歌星和兄弟亨利·考沃德 (Henry Coward) 和霍华德·考沃德 (Howard Coward) 兄弟（由科斯特洛和 T Bone 饰演）的历史，他们痛苦地回忆起自己在音乐行业的经历，包括被残酷的经理骗走版税，并被说服伪造自己的死亡。</p><p>该系列将于 11 月 21 日在 Audible 上首播，并附有两位音乐家制作的包含 20 首曲目的新专辑。您可以<a href="http://newwst.com/cowardbrothers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订专辑并查看下面的第一首单曲“Always”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="胆小鬼兄弟 [Elvis Costello &amp; T Bone Burnett] - Always（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WpWmf2fmjqk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p>科斯特洛在一份新闻稿中表示：“关于霍华德·考沃德这个人和我是同一个人的荒谬断言，我不得不说：这是一个骗子、圆桌骗子和江湖骗子的作品，我将立即研究我的法律选择。”</p><p>与此同时，T Bone 补充道：“我模糊地记得很多年前，我购买了一个名为 The Coward Brothers 的乐队的歌曲《Pure Bubblegum》的 45 张。我在沃斯堡一家名为 KXOL 的广播电台听到了这首歌，该电台被宣传为“新音乐”。唱片骑师播放过一次后，听众反响很差，以至于第二天早上他们在电台前把它烧掉了。那些家伙到底发生了什么——他们还活着吗？” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DA3n1PAuSph/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 5